579
00:24:05,520 --> 00:24:07,520
Chairman Wang is here.

580
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:08,320
Any instructions?

581
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:09,920
Let's talk inside.

582
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:10,720
No, stay right here.

583
00:24:11,600 --> 00:24:13,680
I'm here to submit a bail submission.

584
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:15,280
Who wants to pay the bail?

585
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:18,080
I, Wang Chonghui, and Lin Changmin

586
00:24:18,320 --> 00:24:20,800
wish to bail the 32 arrested students arrested.

587
00:24:18,630 --> 00:24:20,546
[Wang Daxie, styled Botang, Chairman of the Foreign Affairs Committee of the Republic of China]

588
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,520
This is the bail petition.

589
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:26,960
Let me read it to you.

590
00:24:27,040 --> 00:24:28,000
No, I'll read it for myself.

591
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:28,800
Wu Bingxiang,

592
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:30,480
are you going to listen or not?

593
00:24:31,520 --> 00:24:31,840
I will listen.

594
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:32,480
I'm listening.

595
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,520
I'm all ears.

596
00:24:39,360 --> 00:24:40,160
On the fourth day of this month,

597
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:41,520
students from various schools in Beijing

598
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,440
called for diplomatic issues.

599
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:46,000
The gathering of people led to the brewing incident

600
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,160
in the noisy fields at the time.

601
00:24:48,560 --> 00:24:50,400
More than 30 students were arrested.

602
00:24:50,800 --> 00:24:52,880
It is sad to see people brought the actions into excesses for a good cause.

603
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,000
For their patriotism.

604
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:56,160
And the more than 30 people,

605
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,000
who may not be the perpetrators,

606
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:01,040
Daxie, along with others, beg to bail them.

607
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,560
If you need these ones for interrogation in the future.

608
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:05,360
We bear the responsibility to deliver them to the court.

609
00:25:05,760 --> 00:25:08,400
People's anger is getting closer to the limit any minute now.

610
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:11,520
For this reason, it is urgent for this bail to be granted.

611
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:13,600
With respect on behalf of the people.

612
00:25:14,320 --> 00:25:15,840
Thus is presented to the police chief.

613
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:17,520
Presenters:

614
00:25:17,920 --> 00:25:18,480
Wang Daxie,

615
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:19,600
Wang Chonghui,

616
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:21,120
Lin Changmin.

617
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:34,640
Chairman Wang,

618
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:37,600
I'll take your bail submission.

619
00:25:41,840 --> 00:25:42,880
However,

620
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:44,880
for the release of students,

621
