00:26:28,240 --> 00:26:28,720
How old are you?

636
00:26:29,280 --> 00:26:29,840
Twenty-nine.

637
00:26:29,353 --> 00:26:31,859
[Xu Deheng, styled Chusheng, Student at Peking University]

638
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:31,920
Such a treasurous young man.

639
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:35,840
How can you commit murder and arson?

640
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:38,560
We did nothing but treasure our country.

641
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,280
It's neither murder nor arson.

642
00:26:41,600 --> 00:26:42,320
Patriotism?

643
00:26:44,800 --> 00:26:46,320
You think you are patriotic?

644
00:26:47,360 --> 00:26:47,840
Xu Deheng,

645
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:51,440
I just want to ask you one question.

646
00:26:52,240 --> 00:26:53,680
You marched in the streets.

647
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:56,400
Who is behind this?

648
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:58,720
My head grows on my shoulder.

649
00:26:59,280 --> 00:27:01,120
Do I need to be instructed by others?

650
00:27:04,080 --> 00:27:05,200
But I heard

651
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:07,520
that you are a loyal follower to Li Dazhao

652
00:27:07,840 --> 00:27:09,920
