655
00:27:16,960 --> 00:27:18,000
Tell me about it.

656
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:20,560
What have they told you recently?

657
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:21,680
Come and drink.

658
00:27:23,760 --> 00:27:24,960
Chief Wu.

659
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,560
You flatter me.

660
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:29,200
Chen Duxiu is a famous scholar in China.

661
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,440
Li Dazhao is the director of the library.

662
00:27:32,320 --> 00:27:33,760
I am just an ordinary student.

663
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:35,920
I can't even meet them casually.

664
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,840
How can I know what they said?

665
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:59,360
Xu Deheng, you know,

666
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:02,080
the reason I came to ask you myself today

667
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,320
is to give you a way out.

668
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:06,320
Why don't you cooperate?

669
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:09,040
I really want to cooperate with you, Chief Wu.

670
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:11,520
I told the whole truth and only the truth.

671
00:28:11,920 --> 00:28:13,280
