672
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,160
as a way to cooperate.

673
00:28:14,320 --> 00:28:14,960
Take him.

674
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:15,520
Yes.

675
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:26,800
Come in

676
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,880
Result?

677
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:33,440
These students are all in cahoots.

678
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,360
Confessions are all the same.

679
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,400
Interrogate them all tonight.

680
00:28:45,760 --> 00:28:47,680
Be sure to dig out the mastermind behind it.

681
00:28:50,320 --> 00:28:50,720
Yes.

682
00:28:57,600 --> 00:29:00,160
The situation has changed dramatically since May 5th.

683
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:03,760
The Beijing National Foreign Affairs Association, the Chamber of Commerce, and the Farmers Association

684
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:06,640
all sent letters to the government and put words out around the country,

685
00:29:07,840 --> 00:29:08,960
that they support the student movement

686
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:11,120
and request the release of the arrested students.

687
00:29:11,440 --> 00:29:14,000
Sun Wen, Linsen and Tang Shaoyi in the Southern government

688
00:29:14,480 --> 00:29:16,480
along with Kang Youwei, Wu Peifu, Zhang Jingyao,

689
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:18,880
Chen Guangyuan and others expressed their support for the students,

690
00:29:19,280 --> 00:29:22,080
demanding to remove Cao Rulin, Zhang Zongxiang, and Lu Zongyu from duty.

691
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:24,960
There are several senators in Congress

692
00:29:25,120 --> 00:29:26,720
who have jointly sent a letter to the President

693
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,720
requesting the release of the arrested students.

694
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,080
Besides Beijing and Guangzhou,

695
00:29:30,560 --> 00:29:30,880
Shanghai,

696
