Nanjing,

697
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:32,000
Tianjin,

698
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:32,560
Wuhan,

699
00:29:32,720 --> 00:29:33,120
Changsha,

700
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,920
activities in support of Beijing students also took place.

701
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,200
In the last two days,

702
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,640
the Presidential Palace and the State Council

703
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:41,520
have received messages of support.

704
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:42,800
More than one hundred of them.

705
00:29:43,360 --> 00:29:45,280
Solidarity activities around the country show the following characteristics:

706
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:47,680
One, setting up student organizations

707
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:50,320
to implement various action plans.

708
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,080
Two, organizing demonstrations

709
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:54,160
to protest the government's foreign policy,

710
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:56,400
the Paris Peace Treaty and the arrest of the students.

711
00:29:56,800 --> 00:29:58,960
Three, a full-scale boycott of Japanese goods.

712
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:00,240
All these indicate that

713
00:30:00,560 --> 00:30:03,200
the government's crisis of trust has taken shape in an all-round way.

714
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:06,400
All right, all right, that's enough.

715
00:30:07,120 --> 00:30:08,080
Everyone,

716
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:11,520
what countermeasures should we take?

717
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,160
Mr. President,

718
00:30:24,320 --> 00:30:27,040
this is my third resignation letter.

719
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:31,040
I'm incompetent in carrying on my duty.

720
00:30:31,520 --> 00:30:32,480
Please approve.

721
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:36,320
Fu Zengxiang, this is not your resignation.

722
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,240
This is blackmail.

723
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,040
At this time, you have to pick a fault.

724
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:42,320
No way.

725
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,560
I can resign without resigning.

726
00:30:47,360 --> 00:30:49,120
Then let the arrested students go.

727
00:30:49,600 --> 00:30:51,120
The students have been on strike for two days.

728
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:52,720
If it continues,

729
00:30:53,120 --> 00:30:54,720
the situation will be unmanageable.

730
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:55,920
No way.

731
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,560
General Duan said that students can't go.

732
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,400
Cao Rulin has to stay in his position either.

733
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,920
Nonsense.

734
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:03,440
We have guns in our hands.

735
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,760
What harm can a few students do?

736
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,920
Who says they can't do harm.

737
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:09,760
The city of Beijing

738
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,840
has been turned upside down by students.

739
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:15,120
Do you know what the students are going to do?

740
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:17,840
They intend to launch a general mobilization to the whole society.

741
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,520
The newly established Beijing Federation of Students

742
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,960
are going to the streets,

743
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:24,800
going to the streets and the factories to give speeches.

744
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:27,760
They also plan to go to Shanghai, Wuhan, Changsha and other places.

745
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,880
Giving speeches,

746
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:31,360
planning to establish the National Federation of Students.

747
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,440
Now it's more than just the academics.

748
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:35,600
They also encouraged the business community.

749
00:31:35,920 --> 00:31:38,160
Seeing that the military community is also dividing,

750
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,520
when May 7th comes,

751
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:41,600
as soon as the Central Park National Convention opens,

752
00:31:42,080 --> 00:31:44,160
it will for sure be a volcanic eruption.

753
00:31:44,560 --> 00:31:45,360
By then,

754
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:47,920
there's nothing you can do to help.

755
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:49,760
Chief Wu,

756
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:52,560
you are exaggerating.

757
00:31:53,600 --> 00:31:54,000
Mr. President,

758
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:56,640
whether I am exaggerating or not,

759
00:31:57,280 --> 00:31:59,120
please listen to the Premier's opinion.

760
00:32:01,760 --> 00:32:02,160
Premier Qian,

761
