766
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:19,680
I only have one strategy,

767
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:22,320
release the arrested students.

768
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:26,160
That will be slapping our faces.

769
00:32:26,640 --> 00:32:29,040
Besides, what about General Duan's will?

770
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:32,400
Mr. President,

771
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:36,400
all I can say now is to release students.

772
00:32:37,200 --> 00:32:39,200
If you must not let them go,

773
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:41,680
if there is any trouble in Beijing again,

774
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,200
I can't take the responsibility.

775
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:45,840
I also resign.

776
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:48,800
Jingtan,

777
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:57,360
don't be like a child now.

778
00:32:58,480 --> 00:32:59,280
You come back.

779
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:01,280
Come back and sit down.

780
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:15,120
Premier Qian, you are the Premier of the State.

781
00:33:15,600 --> 00:33:17,200
What do you think you should do?

782
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,720
My opinion

783
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,600
is exactly the same as Chief Wu's.

784
00:33:26,160 --> 00:33:26,720
I see.

785
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:29,120
I see.

786
00:33:29,760 --> 00:33:31,280
Since you are all share the same opinion,

787
00:33:32,080 --> 00:33:33,760
I can agree to release the students.

788
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:36,560
But I have to ask you to be aware of two things.

789
00:33:37,120 --> 00:33:40,000
First, make sure that in all schools,

790
00:33:40,320 --> 00:33:41,840
all classes must resume on May 7th.

791
00:33:42,560 --> 00:33:44,960
Second, ensure that all students and teachers

792
00:33:45,040 --> 00:33:47,440
