793
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:49,360
on May 7th.

794
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:52,800
If anything goes wrong, I'll hold you all accountable.

795
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:57,600
Go ahead with the discussion.

796
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:21,600
Students!

797
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:24,080
In response to appeals from all walks of life,

798
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,720
with great kindness, the President

799
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:29,680
ordered to spare you for your recklessness.

800
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:33,440
We will also send cars to take you back to school.

801
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:36,880
I hope you can be grateful to the government.

802
00:34:37,600 --> 00:34:39,680
Focus on study and stop making trouble.

803
00:34:40,480 --> 00:34:40,960
Please.

804
00:35:01,520 --> 00:35:02,480
Fellow students.

805
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:05,520
Principal Cai came in personal to pick you up.

806
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:06,640
Please.

807
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:12,320
Mr. Cai.

808
00:35:16,160 --> 00:35:16,720
Mr. Zhongfu.

809
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,000
Chief Wu.

810
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:24,720
