824
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,560
Your spirit,

825
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:21,440
I admire it very much.

826
00:36:22,160 --> 00:36:24,000
But I want you to know.

827
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:26,160
In order to rescue you,

