Students, don't let down

834
00:36:45,040 --> 00:36:46,320
hundreds of thousands of teachers and students in Beijing

835
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,880
with their sincere hearts.

836
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,920
Mr. Cai, you don't have to persuade us.

837
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:54,000
We appreciate your help.

838
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,960
I also yearn for a free life outside prison.

839
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:00,160
But, as long as it can awaken the Chinese people

840
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:02,400
even if we give our lives away,

841
00:37:03,360 --> 00:37:04,560
we're willing to do it.

842
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:39,200
You-

843
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:40,960
You kids

844
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:43,920
are just so arrogant.

845
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:45,840
You think

846
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:47,680
to wake up a nation

847
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:49,600
trapped in a feudal mindset

848
00:37:49,680 --> 00:37:51,360
for thousands of years

849
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:53,040
is that easy?

850
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,040
You think

851
00:37:55,520 --> 00:37:57,040
to wipe out the numbness, indifference,

852
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,600
and inert thinking

853
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:01,040
from the blood of our nation

854
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,560
is a day's work?

855
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:05,680
It will take several generations

856
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,920
to strive for a great cause.

857
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,640
Let me tell you.

858
00:38:11,440 --> 00:38:13,920
You have no right to die now.

859
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:17,040
This disaster-stricken country of ours

860
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,720
needs you stay alive,

861
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:20,800
needs you to fight!

862
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:35,360
Mr. Zhongfu.

863
00:38:36,080 --> 00:38:36,880
We'll go with you.

864
00:39:46,640 --> 00:39:48,880
So this is how you brought them back.

865
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:54,400
It's your style.

866
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:58,160
But sometimes you can be a bit bossy.

867
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:01,520
Am I?

868
00:40:03,200 --> 00:40:03,920
I'm not overbearing.

869
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:05,600
They are confused.

870
00:40:06,320 --> 00:40:07,040
Revolutionaries.

871
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:10,320
They can't do such a thing as killing themselves in the revolution?

872
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,920
You can be an alarm if you want,

873
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:15,040
but you have to respect a bomb's will to go without regret.

874
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,240
What do you mean?

875
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:17,600
For example,

876
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,520
there is this land

877
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:21,600
where a group of people are sleeping.

878
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:23,120
In the distance, there is a volcano

879
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,720
about to explode.

880
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,000
You are like an alarm clock.

881
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:27,840
Facing these sleeping people,

882
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:29,840
you want to wake them up.

883
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,840
So you keep ringing.

884
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:33,440
The ones sleeping lightly,

885
00:40:34,240 --> 00:40:34,960
you woke them up.

886
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,880
They go with you to wake up the others.

887
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:38,960
But there are too many people,

888
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:40,880
your voice is too weak.

889
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,520
After all, there are only a few people who awaken.

890
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:44,800
And sometimes,

891
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:46,400
there are ones find you as a nuisance.

892
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:48,080
From time to time, they kick the alarm away.

893
00:40:48,800 --> 00:40:51,120
Then there are alarm clocks that are afraid of being too late.

894
00:40:51,680 --> 00:40:52,800
So they use their lives

895
00:40:53,760 --> 00:40:54,560
as raw material

896
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:56,080
to turn into a bomb.

897
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:58,880
The explosion will awaken a large number of people.

898
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,720
Then, as you say,

899
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:03,120
the bomb is much more powerful than the alarm clock.

900
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,600
So all we need is few more bombs?

901
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:06,960
What's the use of an alarm clock then?

902
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:08,400
No.

903
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:11,920
Brother Zhongfu, think about it.

904
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:15,680
If it was not for the alarm clock

905
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:19,040
that kept ringing constantly and never stopped,

906
00:41:19,680 --> 00:41:21,360
there wouldn't be any bomb.

907
00:41:21,920 --> 00:41:23,280
Although the bomb is powerful,

908
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:26,640
it can't overcome people's inertia after all.

909
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,320
Only the alarm clock

910
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:31,360
keeps ringing, keeps reminding, keeps watching

911
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:34,640
to finally wake everyone up.
